OL,3,CMan hallucinated about 'bears and
OL,4,Cburglars' after taking eye medication
OL,6,FA man was not warned about the side-
OL,7,Feffects of a new medicine before he
OL,8,Fsuffered a psychotic episode which led
OL,9,Fto him having hallucinations of bears
OL,10,Fand burglars, a watchdog has said.
OL,12,FThe Parliamentary and Health Service
OL,13,FOmbudsman (PHSO) said Andrew Holland
OL,14,Fwas "not fully informed" when he was
OL,15,Fprescribed prednisolone ` a type of
OL,16,Fsteroid.
OL,18,FMr Holland suffered a psychotic
OL,19,Fepisode which lasted for weeks after
OL,20,Fhe was prescribed the drug at in 2022
OL,21,Fto treat inflammation in his eye.
