OL,3,CMan hallucinated about 'bears and
OL,4,Cburglars' after taking eye medication
OL,6,FThe 61-year-old, from began suffering
OL,7,Fdisrupted sleep and severe headaches
OL,8,Fafter starting the drug.
OL,10,FHe then became aggressive, psychotic
OL,11,Fand was "inexplicably wandering the
OL,12,Fstreet at different times of the day
OL,13,Fand night", the PHSO said.
OL,15,FMr Holland began seeing hallucinations
OL,16,Fwhich left him "confused and scared",
OL,17,Fthe ombudsman added.
