OL,3,CMan hallucinated about 'bears and
OL,4,Cburglars' after taking eye medication
OL,6,F"I was seeing all sorts... there was a
OL,7,Fbear at the end of the garden one day
OL,8,Fand a burglar coming over the garage
OL,9,Froof," Mr Holland said.
OL,11,F"I just took what they told me to
OL,12,Ftake. I wouldn't like to go through
OL,13,Fthat again and I wouldn't wish it on
OL,14,Fanyone either."
OL,16,FAfter several hospital visits for
OL,17,Fsymptoms, he was diagnosed with
OL,18,Fsteroid-induced psychosis, and later
OL,19,Fsteroid mania.
