OL,3,CMan hallucinated about 'bears and
OL,4,Cburglars' after taking eye medication
OL,6,FThe PHSO said there was a "missed
OL,7,Fopportunity to fully inform (Mr
OL,8,FHolland) of potential extreme side-
OL,9,Feffects" of his medication and it
OL,10,Frecommended that Manchester University
OL,11,FNHS Foundation Trust pay #700
OL,12,Fcompensation in recognition of the
OL,13,Fdistress and worry he experienced.
OL,15,FPHSO chief executive Rebecca
OL,16,FHilsenrath said: "This must have been
OL,17,Fa terrifying experience. It is an act
OL,18,Fof trust to put yourself under the
OL,19,Fcare of others, and trust depends on
OL,20,Finformation and understanding.
