OL,6,F"No-one wants to suffer a psychotic
OL,7,Fepisode ` no-one should do so as a
OL,8,Fresult of medication without fully
OL,9,Funderstanding and accepting the risk."
OL,11,FPatient safety information leaflets
OL,12,Ffor prednisolone tablets (1mg and 5mg)
OL,13,Fstate that "mental health problems can
OL,14,Fhappen while taking steroids like
OL,15,Fprednisolone".
