OL,3,CMan hallucinated about 'bears and
OL,4,Cburglars' after taking eye medication
OL,6,FThe leaflet adds: "Steroids including
OL,7,Fprednisolone can cause serious mental
OL,8,Fhealth problems. These are common in
OL,9,Fboth adults and children. They can
OL,10,Faffect about five in every 100 people
OL,11,Ftaking medicines like prednisolone
OL,12,Ftablets."
OL,14,FThese can include feeling, seeing or
OL,15,Fhearing things which do not exist and
OL,16,Fhaving strange and frightening
OL,17,Fthoughts.
OL,19,FManchester University NHS Foundation
OL,20,FTrust has been approached for comment.
